Ya ayyuha allatheena amanoo la tuqaddimoo bayna yadayi Allahi warasoolihi waittaqoo Allaha inna Allaha samee’un ‘aleemun
Ya ayyuha allatheena amanoo la tarfa’oo aswatakum fawqa sawti alnnabiyyi wala tajharoo lahu bialqawli kajahri ba’dikum liba’din an tahbata a’malukum waantum la tash’uroona
Inna allatheena yaghuddoona aswatahum ‘inda rasooli Allahi ola-ika allatheena imtahana Allahu quloobahum lilttaqwa lahum maghfiratun waajrun ‘atheemun
Inna allatheena yunadoonaka min wara-i alhujurati aktharuhum la ya’qiloona
Walaw annahum sabaroo hatta takhruja ilayhim lakana khayran lahum waAllahu ghafoorun raheemun
Ya ayyuha allatheena amanoo in jaakum fasiqun binaba-in fatabayyanoo an tuseeboo qawman bijahalatin fatusbihoo ‘ala ma fa’altum nadimeena
Wai’lamoo anna feekum rasoola Allahi law yutee’ukum fee katheerin mina al-amri la’anittum walakinna Allaha habbaba ilaykumu al-eemana wazayyanahu fee quloobikum wakarraha ilaykumu alkufra waalfusooqa waal’isyana ola-ika humu alrrashidoona
Fadlan mina Allahi wani’matan waAllahu ‘aleemun hakeemun
Wa-in ta-ifatani mina almu/mineena iqtataloo faaslihoo baynahuma fa-in baghat ihdahuma ‘ala al-okhra faqatiloo allatee tabghee hatta tafee-a ila amri Allahi fa-in faat faaslihoo baynahuma bial’adli waaqsitoo inna Allaha yuhibbu almuqsiteena
Innama almu/minoona ikhwatun faaslihoo bayna akhawaykum waittaqoo Allaha la’allakum turhamoona
Ya ayyuha allatheena amanoo la yaskhar qawmun min qawmin ‘asa an yakoonoo khayran minhum wala nisaon min nisa-in ‘asa an yakunna khayran minhunna wala talmizoo anfusakum wala tanabazoo bial-alqabi bi/sa al-ismu alfusooqu ba’da aleemani waman lam yatub faola-ika humu alththalimoona
Ya ayyuha allatheena amanoo ijtaniboo katheeran mina alththanni inna ba’da alththanni ithmun wala tajassasoo wala yaghtab ba’dukum ba’dan ayuhibbu ahadukum an ya/kula lahma akheehi maytan fakarihtumoohu waittaqoo Allaha inna Allaha tawwabun raheemun
Ya ayyuha alnnasu inna khalaqnakum min thakarin waontha waja’alnakum shu’ooban waqaba-ila lita’arafoo inna akramakum ‘inda Allahi atqakum inna Allaha ‘aleemun khabeerun
Qalati al-a’rabu amanna qul lam tu/minoo walakin qooloo aslamna walamma yadkhuli al-eemanu fee quloobikum wa-in tutee’oo Allaha warasoolahu la yalitkum min a’malikum shay-an inna Allaha ghafoorun raheemun
Innama almu/minoona allatheena amanoo biAllahi warasoolihi thumma lam yartaboo wajahadoo bi-amwalihim waanfusihim fee sabeeli Allahi ola-ika humu alssadiqoona
Qul atu’allimoona Allaha bideenikum waAllahu ya’lamu ma fee alssamawati wama fee al-ardi waAllahu bikulli shay-in ‘aleemun
Yamunnoona ‘alayka an aslamoo qul la tamunnoo ‘alayya islamakum bali Allahu yamunnu ‘alaykum an hadakum lil-eemani in kuntum sadiqeena
Inna Allaha ya’lamu ghayba alssamawati waal-ardi waAllahu baseerun bima ta’maloona